      <scopecontent id="aspace_83d292d5294273249bf42c2ea84fd384">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, financial records, and printed material documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Department of Geography, which no longer exists as a separate academic unit.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
